Octociz regains conciousness. He had been trained to a trolly, and 
was being wheeled out. Bronco, at the front, laughed.

"Looks like no one cares about you. In 2 mega-cycles, I'm gonna blow 
ya to bits if I don't get my computer. You better pray that the 
Maximals do something."

Octociz began to lose hope as he neared the site where the Axalon 
fell into the sea.
